✅ 1. Daily Backup Script

📂 Requirement
Take backup of /home
Store in /backup
Keep date-wise backups



vim daily_backup.sh
#!/bin/bash

SRC="/home"
DEST="/backup"
DATE=$(date +%F)

mkdir -p $DEST
tar -czf $DEST/home_backup_$DATE.tar.gz $SRC

echo "Backup completed on $DATE" >> /var/log/backup.log



⏰ Cron Job
0 2 * * * /bin/bash /root/scripts/daily_backup.sh

