✅ 2. Log Cleanup Script

📂 Requirement
Delete .log files older than 7 days
Path: /var/log


vim log_cleanup.sh

#!/bin/bash

LOG_DIR="/var/log"
DAYS=7

find $LOG_DIR -type f -name "*.log" -mtime +$DAYS -exec rm -f {} \;

echo "Old logs deleted older than $DAYS days" >> /var/log/cleanup.log

⏰ Cron Job
0 3 * * * /bin/bash /root/scripts/log_cleanup.sh

