✅ 3. User Creation Script (Automation)
📂 Requirement
Create user with password
Ask username from admin


vm user_create.sh
#!/bin/bash

read -p "Enter username: " USER
read -s -p "Enter password: " PASS
echo

useradd $USER
echo "$USER:$PASS" | chpasswd

echo "User $USER created successfully"
