✅ 4. Disk Usage Alert Script (with Mail)

📂 Requirement
Alert if disk usage > 80%
Send mail to admin

vim disk_alert.sh

#!/bin/bash

THRESHOLD=80
EMAIL="admin@example.com"

USAGE=$(df / | awk 'NR==2 {print $5}' | sed 's/%//')

if [ $USAGE -gt $THRESHOLD ]; then
    echo "Disk usage is $USAGE%" | mail -s "Disk Alert on Server" $EMAIL
fi


⏰ Cron Job
*/30 * * * * /bin/bash /root/scripts/disk_alert.sh

