✅ 5. CPU & Memory Monitoring Script

📂 Requirement
Check CPU & RAM
Send alert if high usage


vim cpu_mem_monitor.sh

#!/bin/bash

CPU=$(top -bn1 | grep "Cpu(s)" | awk '{print $2 + $4}')
MEM=$(free | awk '/Mem/ {printf("%.0f"), $3/$2 * 100}')
EMAIL="admin@example.com"

if [ $CPU -gt 80 ] || [ $MEM -gt 80 ]; then
    echo "High Usage Alert
CPU: $CPU%
Memory: $MEM%" | mail -s "CPU/Memory Alert" $EMAIL
fi



⏰ Cron Job
*/10 * * * * /bin/bash /root/scripts/cpu_mem_monitor.sh
